{"tid":269231,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助] windows要點同時用幾個device出聲","createTime":"2017-06-03T15:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T06:01:09.000Z","uid":54481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af31f996429a8cba2bf3de08aef7bae140b37345","tid":269231,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> help<br />\n<br />\n岩岩回歸windows，發現windows唔可以幾個device一齊出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmac果邊有個software叫&quot;audio hijack&quot;可以自己set<br />\n我google完發現有舊野叫stereo mixer<br />\n但係完全唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我要出聲既暫時有兩件野<br />\n1.) HDMI mon speaker<br />\n2.) USB 7.1 headset<br />\n<br />\n兩件個stereo mixer都pick up唔到任何野<br />\n跟住我又試左用3.5mm耳筒，個stereo mixer終於pickup到<br />\n但係無論隻mon定係個usb headset都冇聲出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a277ac247de1d9360797b9f2b13d823693a06f10","tid":269231,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24133469164c6c90928e07e32c313aff05b43a6b","tid":269231,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77f7967faf1df16aa98e3c6df34fbf68593978e","tid":269231,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"留名等學嘢"},{"pid":"a5a83070fda32ffc8295858c122e3db894ced386","tid":269231,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":